CANONICAL RUNTIME PATH
- invoked by: remote-executor.mjs
- public operator cli: ./skyequanta -> skyequanta.mjs
- one-command operator path: ./START_HERE.sh -> START_HERE.sh
- launcher: ./skyequanta start -> apps/skyequanta-shell/bin/launch.mjs
- bridge/runtime: ./skyequanta bridge:start -> apps/skyequanta-shell/bin/bridge.mjs
- workspace manager: apps/skyequanta-shell/lib/workspace-manager.mjs
- executor: apps/skyequanta-shell/bin/remote-executor.mjs
- proof runner: apps/skyequanta-shell/bin/workspace-proof-section3-truthpath.mjs
- deploy runner: apps/skyequanta-shell/bin/doctor.mjs
- docs: docs/CANONICAL_RUNTIME_PATHS.md
